{"tid":2423444,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"有市民接種科興疫苗後稱開心舒服　有人形容過程輕鬆暢順","createTime":"2021-02-26T02:15:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-26T03:05:55.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"fc7c63fa4be5383dea9cb54d189b36a4c26de96d","tid":2423444,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T02:15:56.000Z","msg":"本港今日正式展開新冠疫苗接種計劃，其中在銅鑼灣中央圖書館的疫苗接種中心，陸續有已預約的優先群組市民前來接種科興疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n有人接種疫苗後後豎起拇指，表示接種後開心舒服，針口並無不適，形容整個流程暢順，人員講解非常專業，讚揚百分百滿意政府安排，又說等候了一段時間，終於等到國家疫苗抵港。<br />\n<br />\n亦有人形容接種疫苗過程輕鬆，流程暢順，有人介紹接種疫苗的注意事項，接種後獲安排到專區休息。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1577621-20210226.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1577621-20210226.htm&d=6DLEtCU0DjtZYWozPjwd6wfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=08f1159a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1577621-20210226.htm&h=fc0990fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1577621-20210226.htm</a>"},{"pid":"fb2f859772136b54b48dd8fa27dbf83f7bfb3eea","tid":2423444,"uid":310311,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T02:17:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又係打白粉針咁個個又開心又舒服"},{"pid":"d84029f0a5b9f910a6cb40801c07ee74a2890243","tid":2423444,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T02:19:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static-stheadline-com.cdn.ampproject.org/i/s/static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20210226/_2021022608585737572.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic-stheadline-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fi%2Fs%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20210226%2F_2021022608585737572.jpg&h=591bf89c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有排隊等候的長者表示，期待接種疫苗已久，因為相信國家的出品，加上為令自己安心，決定第一時間預約接種；有長者還期望接種後，能早日北上時免檢疫。另有長期病患者和任職醫護人員的排隊人士均表示，科興疫苗副作用較少，希望接種後能保護自己。<br />\n<br />\n市民接種後都獲發針卡，有長者開心地表示，接種流程暢順，也有職員講解注意事項，會向親友推介接種。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hd.stheadline. com/news/realtime/hk/2008140</code></pre>"},{"pid":"aa6389011eda2a0c2b56594cd50e2cb7eebb10ae","tid":2423444,"uid":134182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T02:20:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40acdd8b73b369969f684f608e504049f2e70d4d","tid":2423444,"uid":70786,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T02:23:38.000Z","msg":"快d中武肺俾內鬼抗體整到肺爛<br />\n全身免疫細胞風暴插人工心肺都救唔撚翻<br />\n最後痛苦至極咁落地獄等林鄭<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89d722f522fa7ea036371c14e5057f8c03d95421","tid":2423444,"uid":15830,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T02:24:31.000Z","msg":"打針打到有幻覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e20c5e5b5e6e99b1bc35126bc32e6858cac5537","tid":2423444,"uid":276273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T02:26:44.000Z","msg":"人死之前，通常都迴光返照，RAP"},{"pid":"24e881f2f295fd34805f14303ea550d6355e0183","tid":2423444,"uid":127929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T02:27:36.000Z","msg":"安樂死<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6fe6b2bc8d5a2dd400ce6e450381d8d6dd71919","tid":2423444,"uid":83865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T02:43:50.000Z","msg":"點解個個打完會興奮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地係唔係打錯針<br />\n<br />\n我打完疫苗要瞓足一日"},{"pid":"0b5fc4972e853346e01c8efba10acabe412676fd","tid":2423444,"uid":38757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T02:53:39.000Z","msg":"唔係好明.... <br />\n明知科興得5成幾有效, <br />\n打完同之前一樣又要戴口罩, 打黎都係無用<br />\n寧願等其他好過...."},{"pid":"e30a809539af30b5acc2e3a4bd7084de8eb8135b","tid":2423444,"uid":59242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T03:02:39.000Z","msg":"侮辱區旗呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />拉得<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過愛國愛黨唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c02595fc66ccdc82728e644bfc1c1e7a15bae16","tid":2423444,"uid":169801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T03:05:55.000Z","msg":"睇錯注射後身心舒暢，以為講緊毒品<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}